relation_UNIT_NET
query:
LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM 'file:///UNIT_NET.csv' AS row
MATCH (a:Unit{unitId: row.UNITID})
MATCH (b:Netname{netId: row.NETID})
MERGE (a)-[:UNIT_NET]->(b);

name: relation_QUESTIONNET

LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM 'file:///net_question.csv' AS row
MATCH (a:Question{questionId: row.question_id})
MATCH (b:Netname{netId: row.net_id})
MERGE (a)-[:QUESTIONNET]->(b);
